These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, polish, nigerian, indonesian, chinese, colombian
1. the indonesian is between the polish and the argentine##2
2. the chinese is on the right of the malaysian##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the chinese is in the middle##1
5. the argentine is in an odd position##4
6. the polish is on the left of the indonesian##1
7. the malaysian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | malaysian | chinese | polish | indonesian | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, surfing, ice-hockey, cricket, baseball, parkour, swimming
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Sport   | baseball | basketball | parkour | surfing | cricket | ice-hockey | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, fisherman, dancer, social-worker, designer, dressmaker
1. the fisherman is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the accountant is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the librarian is on the left or right of the dancer##3
4. the social-worker is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
5. the dancer is on the left of the accountant##1
6. the accountant is on the left of the social-worker##1
7. the fisherman is in an even position##4
8. the accountant is on the left of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Job   | librarian | dancer | accountant | social-worker | dressmaker | fisherman | designer |

