.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, parkour, badminton, weightlifting, water-polo, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | cricket | surfing | weightlifting | rugby | water-polo | badminton | parkour |

