.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, soy-milk, 7up, juice, tea, almond-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
| Beverage   | coffee | 7up | juice | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | tea |

