.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-9::.
7 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog, pony, dog, rat
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |     3      |   4    |   5    |  6   |   7   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | rat | mouse | pony | dog | bird | hedgehog |

