.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, bus, roller, helicopter, skateboard, van, trike
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 8. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Transport   | bus | car | trike | helicopter | skateboard | roller | van |

 